### Layout Components

Layouts should be designed in Figma and extracted using Bumba Design features:

1. Design shell layouts in Figma
2. Extract via Bumba plugin
3. Transform to {{framework}} using `/design-transform-{{framework}}`

The shell should include:
- Navigation component (sidebar, top bar, or minimal)
- Layout container for section content
- User menu/profile access
- Responsive behavior for mobile/tablet/desktop
