## Responsive Behavior

The shell should adapt to different screen sizes:
- **Mobile**: Collapsible navigation, hamburger menu
- **Tablet**: Adaptive navigation (icon + label or collapsible)
- **Desktop**: Full navigation chrome

## Accessibility

- Keyboard navigation support (Tab, Arrow keys, Enter)
- ARIA labels for navigation items
- Skip to content link
- Focus indicators

